## Conventions

- Every assumption is **explicit** (no implicit assumptions) — if it's load-bearing, it's logged.
- Every assumption has a **verification plan** (how do we know it's true?).
- Every assumption has a **confidence** (≈X%).
- Every assumption has a **status**: pending | verified | falsified | superseded.
- If an assumption is falsified, log the impact + remediation in `tracking/decisions.md`.
- Falsified assumptions on critical-severity items trigger HITL escalation immediately.

